[normal]Europe
[normal] there is a sense that the economy here is doing better.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Q55 [bold]&#xa0; 
[normal]John Mann:[bold] But to be precise, if we compare with the 
[normal]US
[normal], 
[normal]Canada
[normal], German and the 
[normal]Eurozone
[normal], how do you think we are going to do?
